<p>The responsive grid is key in the creation of a responsive website. We use <strong>8 columns in large screens</strong>, and <strong>4 columns in small devices</strong>, with a gutter of 10px. This can be configured in the <em>_config.scss</em> file.</p>

<p>The site has only <strong>one breakpoint at 55em</strong> (550px).</p>
Classes <em>largeN</em> will be active at screens bigger than 550px, and the <em>smallN</em> below that figure, allowing you to have different layouts for the same page, on large and small devices.</p>

<h2>Example of grid for a large device only</h2>
<pre>
	<code>
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;large8 col&quot;&gt;8&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;large1 col&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;large7 col&quot;&gt;7&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;large2 col&quot;&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;large5 col&quot;&gt;5&lt;/div&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;large1 col&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;/div&gt;
	</code>
</pre>

<div class="ductGrid">
<h3>How it looks like</h3>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="large8 col">
			<p class="space1 tomato">8</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="large1 col">
			<p class="space1 tomato">1</p>
		</div>
		<div class="large7 col">
			<p class="space1 tomato">7</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="large2 col">
			<p class="space1 tomato">2</p>
		</div>
		<div class="large5 col">
			<p class="space1 tomato">5</p>
		</div>
		<div class="large1 col">
			<p class="space1 tomato">1</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<p>Note: Additional code added to help visualise the grid.</p>


<h2>Example of variable grid for small and large devices</h2>
<p>Resize your browser to see how the layouts changes.</p>
<pre>
	<code>
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;small4 large8 col&quot;&gt;8&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;small1 large1 col&quot;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;small3 large7 col&quot;&gt;7&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;small4 large4 col&quot;&gt;4&lt;/div&gt;<br/>  &lt;div class=&quot;small4 large4 col&quot;&gt;4&lt;/div&gt;<br/>&lt;/div&gt;
	</code>
</pre>

<div class="ductGrid">
